882
01:32:28,610 --> 01:32:32,040
Battalion 6,
report to Staging Area Alpha.

883
01:32:35,650 --> 01:32:37,049
He's building an army.

884
01:32:38,219 --> 01:32:39,419
Let's go.

885
01:32:39,621 --> 01:32:44,221
All high-level functions,
report immediately to combat stations.

886
01:33:09,984 --> 01:33:12,034
-Goodbye.
-Quorra!

887
01:33:12,754 --> 01:33:15,443
