893
01:34:03,204 --> 01:34:05,103
Well done, sir.

894
01:34:19,554 --> 01:34:21,804
I've never seen anything like it.

895
01:34:22,524 --> 01:34:25,774
Humbly, sir, l know
you have greater designs

896
01:34:26,261 --> 01:34:28,571
