903
01:35:31,726 --> 01:35:34,156
It must have been so lonely out there.

904
01:35:35,730 --> 01:35:38,040
How tragic to be the only one.

905
01:35:40,235 --> 01:35:42,815
I've seen what users
are capable of, Clu.

906
01:35:43,938 --> 01:35:45,958
You don't belong with them.

907
01:35:51,346 --> 01:35:53,896
I have something very special
in mind for you.

908
01:35:57,752 --> 01:35:59,182
Take her upstairs.

909
01:35:59,754 --> 01:36:01,334
And find them.

910
01:36:02,223 --> 01:36:06,473
You'll have to excuse me. You arrived
just as I was preparing a little toast.

911
01:36:22,076 --> 01:36:23,826
Greetings, programs!

912
01:36:27,982 --> 01:36:31,462
Together we have achieved
a great many things.

913
01:36:32,153 --> 01:36:35,693
We have created a vast, complex
system. We've maintained it.

914
01:36:37,458 --> 01:36:39,647
We've improved it.

915
01:36:39,994 --> 01:36:43,473
We have rid it of its imperfection.

916
01:36:45,500 --> 01:36:46,840
Not to mention

917
01:36:47,101 --> 01:36:50,000
rid it of the false deity
who sought to enslave us.

918
01:36:52,740 --> 01:36:54,700
Kevin Flynn!

919
01:36:55,977 --> 01:36:57,706
Where are you now?

920
01:37:01,516 --> 01:37:04,356
My fellow programs,
let there be no doubt

921
01:37:04,786 --> 01:37:07,066
that our world is a cage no more.

922
01:37:07,789 --> 01:37:11,889
For at this moment,
the key to the next frontier is finally

923
01:37:12,660 --> 01:37:14,330
in our possession!

924
01:37:19,734 --> 01:37:21,484
Your disk.

925
01:37:21,769 --> 01:37:23,319
And unlike our selfish Creator,

926
01:37:23,571 --> 01:37:26,881
