only for himself,

927
01:37:27,375 --> 01:37:30,625
I will make their world open

928
01:37:31,145 --> 01:37:33,545
and available to all of us!

929
01:37:36,651 --> 01:37:37,851
Yes!

930
01:37:38,486 --> 01:37:39,976
To all of us!

931
01:37:50,832 --> 01:37:52,122
He's taking all of this with him.

932
01:37:52,834 --> 01:37:54,504
He's figured out how to do it.

933
01:37:54,769 --> 01:37:56,499
And whatever we find there,

934
01:37:56,804 --> 01:37:58,734
there our system will grow!

935
01:37:59,040 --> 01:38:02,230
There our system will blossom!

936
01:38:03,878 --> 01:38:05,248
Do this.

937
01:38:05,480 --> 01:38:07,849
Prove yourselves.
Prove yourselves to me!

938
01:38:08,216 --> 01:38:09,646
Be loyal to me!

939
01:38:10,318 --> 01:38:12,868
And I will never betray you!

940
01:38:25,733 --> 01:38:27,193
Dad, we have to get your disk.

941
01:38:27,502 --> 01:38:29,962
We gotta get to the portal.
You shut them down outside.

942
01:38:30,338 --> 01:38:32,737
Even if make it, you won't
last in here, nor will Quorra.

943
01:38:33,107 --> 01:38:36,007
