944
01:38:37,478 --> 01:38:38,648
Sam...

945
01:38:39,313 --> 01:38:40,923
The same team.

946
01:38:42,016 --> 01:38:43,276
Remember?

947
01:38:45,553 --> 01:38:47,363
l was afraid you were gonna say that.

948
01:38:48,623 --> 01:38:50,522
Meet me on the flight deck in five
and get us some wheels.

949
01:38:50,825 --> 01:38:52,785
