952
01:39:01,235 --> 01:39:03,815
Rid the new system of its imperfection!

953
01:39:06,707 --> 01:39:09,867
My vision is clear, fellow programs.

954
01:39:11,212 --> 01:39:14,902
Out there is a new world!

955
01:39:16,117 --> 01:39:18,517
Out there is our victory!

956
01:39:20,254 --> 01:39:21,624
Out there

957
01:39:23,858 --> 01:39:26,108
