01:43:37,845 --> 01:43:39,685
Death to the user!

981
01:44:04,305 --> 01:44:05,445
Head towards the light, Quorra.

982
01:44:08,442 --> 01:44:10,082
Where did you learn that move?

983
01:44:10,377 --> 01:44:12,717
ENCOM Tower. Couple of nights ago.

984
01:44:15,483 --> 01:44:17,293
ENCOM Tower.

985
01:44:19,920 --> 01:44:21,030
Light jets.

986
01:44:21,722 --> 01:44:22,982
Here they come.

987
01:44:24,024 --> 01:44:25,894
Sam, take the turret.

988
01:44:34,668 --> 01:44:36,748
Man, I'm all over this.

989
01:44:39,940 --> 01:44:40,990
Yeah!

990
01:44:50,985 --> 01:44:53,915
