1001
01:47:04,919 --> 01:47:06,119
Come on.

1002
01:47:09,423 --> 01:47:11,702
Flynn, go!

1003
01:47:15,429 --> 01:47:17,419
Rinzler! Take the shot!

1004
01:47:20,534 --> 01:47:22,084
Finish the game!

1005
01:47:30,110 --> 01:47:31,860
Roll!

1006
01:47:44,458 --> 01:47:46,888
