1040
01:52:38,885 --> 01:52:39,815
Go!

1041
01:52:45,759 --> 01:52:46,749
Dad!

1042
01:52:53,400 --> 01:52:55,330
Sam! It's time!

1043
01:52:55,802 --> 01:52:56,852
No!

1044
01:52:57,337 --> 01:52:59,797
Sam, it's what he wants.

1045
01:53:02,142 --> 01:53:03,871
I'm not leaving you!

1046
01:53:04,478 --> 01:53:05,818
Take her!

1047
01:53:17,424 --> 01:53:18,854
Yes!

1048
01:53:46,687 --> 01:53:48,207
Goodbye, kiddo.

1049
01:54:19,686 --> 01:54:21,385
No!

1050
01:55:32,492 --> 01:55:34,132
Al?

1051
01:55:38,732 --> 01:55:40,372
You paged me?

1052
01:55:41,067 --> 01:55:42,557
Yeah.

1053
01:55:43,503 --> 01:55:45,553
I need you at ENCOM at 8:00 a.m.

1054
01:55:47,741 --> 01:55:49,111
What about the board?

1055
01:55:50,911 --> 01:55:52,641
You're chairman now.

1056
01:55:55,148 --> 01:55:57,338
I'm taking the company back, Alan.

1057
01:56:01,688 --> 01:56:02,798
And...

1058
01:56:04,191 --> 01:56:05,681
You were right.

1059
01:56:07,527 --> 01:56:08,817
About what?

1060
01:56:10,597 --> 01:56:12,027
About everything.

1061
01:56:37,057 --> 01:56:38,227
What's next, Sam?

1062
01:56:44,130 --> 01:56:47,150
I guess we're supposed
to change the world.

1063
01:56:51,571 --> 01:56:54,001
